<li id="cite_note-17"><b><a href="#cite_ref-17" title="">^</a></b> Polar pattern image: Speaker is a <a href="/wiki/Bosch" title="Bosch">Bosch</a> 36 watt <a href="http://www.boschcommunications.us/ProductFamily/Plena%20Public%20Address%20Systems/ProductType/Loudspeakers%20-%20Column/" class="external text" title="http://www.boschcommunications.us/ProductFamily/Plena%20Public%20Address%20Systems/ProductType/Loudspeakers%20-%20Column/" rel="nofollow">LA1-UW36-x columnar model</a> with four identical 4-inch drivers arranged vertically in an enclosure 841 mm (33 inch) high. Polar prediction software is <a href="http://www.clfgroup.org/viewer.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.clfgroup.org/viewer.htm" rel="nofollow">CLF viewer</a>. Loudspeaker information was gathered by the manufacturer into a CF2 file.</li>
