<li id="cite_note-20"><b><a href="#cite_ref-20" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.nxtsound.com/index.php?id=480" class="external text" title="http://www.nxtsound.com/index.php?id=480" rel="nofollow">NXT. <i>Distributed Mode Loudspeaker FAQ</i></a></li>
