<li id="cite_note-22"><b><a href="#cite_ref-22" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.madsci.org/posts/archives/feb98/888372043.Ot.r.html" class="external text" title="http://www.madsci.org/posts/archives/feb98/888372043.Ot.r.html" rel="nofollow">Re: Could You Please Find Research Re:Sound Reproduction Via Gas Flame &amp; Electric</a></li>
</ol>
</div>
